quran[8{c,v,t}:
3,187,"inn ahal kitaab ko woh ehad bhi yaad dlao jo Allah ne un se liya tha ke tumhe kitaab ki talemaat ko logon mein phelana hoga, inhen posheeda rakhna nahi hoga magar unhon ne kitaab ko pas pusht daal diya aur thori qeemat par ussay beech dala kitna bura kaarobar hai jo yeh kar rahay hain"
3,188,tum unn logon ko azaab se mehfooz nah samjhoo jo apne krtoton par khush hain aur chahtay hain ke aisay kamon ki tareef unhen haasil ho jo fi al waqea unhon ne nahi kiye hain haqeeqat mein un ke liye dard naak saza tayyar hai
3,189,zameen aur aasman ka maalik Allah hai aur is ki qudrat sab par haawi hai
3,190,zameen aur asmano ki paidaiesh mein aur raat aur din ke baari baari se anay mein unn hosh mand logon ke liye bohat nishanain hain
3,191,"jo uthte, baithtay aur لlaytay har haal mein khuda ko yaad karte hain aur aasman o zameen ki saakht mein ghhor o fikar karte hain ( woh be ikhtiyar bo l- uthte hain )"" parvar-digaar! yeh sab kuch to ne fuzool aur be maqsad nahi banaya hai, to pak hai is se ke abs kaam kere pas ae rab! hamein dozakh ke azaab se bacha le"
3,192,"to ne jisay dozakh mein dala usay Dur haqeeqat barri zillat o ruswai mein daal diya, aur phir aisay zaalmon ka koi madad gaar nah hoga"
3,193,"maalik! hum ne aik pukarnay walay ko suna jo imaan ki taraf bulaataa tha aur kehta tha ke apne rab ko manu hum ne is ki dawat qubool kar li, pas ae hamaray aaqa! jo qasoor hum se hue hain un se dar guzar farma, jo buraiyan hum mein hain inhen daur kar day aur hamara khtama naik logon ke sath kar"
3,194,"khudawanda! jo waday to ne apne Rasolo-n ke zareya se kiye hain unn ko hamaray sath poora kar aur qayamat ke din hamein ruswai mein nah daal, be shak to apne waday ke khilaaf karne wala nahi hai """
